<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset Request</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
        <h1 style="color: #4a4a4a;">Password Reset Request</h1>
        <p>Dear {{companyName}},</p>
        <p>We received a request to reset your password. If you didn't make this request, please ignore this email.</p>
        <p>To reset your password, use the following token:</p>
        <h2 style="background-color: #f0f0f0; padding: 10px; text-align: center; font-size: 24px;">{{resetToken}}</h2>
        <p>Best regards,<br>The Job Board Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>